teration-001.md:3142:.opencode/commands/spec_kit/assets/spec_kit_deep-review_confirm.yaml:33:  lineage_mode: \\\"[auto|resume|restart] - Session lifecycle intent. Default: auto. The runtime only persists lineage events for `resume` (same sessionId, no archive) and `restart` (new sessionId, generation+1, prior review/ archived). `fork` and `completed-continue` are deferred and no longer accepted — see sk-deep-review/references/loop_protocol.md §Lifecycle Branches.\\\"\\n.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/review/iterations/iteration-002.md:1828:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/review/iterations/iteration-001.md:3150:.opencode/commands/spec_kit/assets/spec_kit_deep-review_confirm.yaml:173:            append_jsonl: '{\\\"type\\\":\\\"event\\\",\\\"event\\\":\\\"resumed\\\",\\\"mode\\\":\\\"review\\\",\\\"sessionId\\\":\\\"{session_id}\\\",\\\"parentSessionId\\\":\\\"{session_id}\\\",\\\"lineageMode\\\":\\\"resume\\\",\\\"continuedFromRun\\\":{iteration_count},\\\"timestamp\\\":\\\"{ISO_8601_NOW}\\\",\\\"generation\\\":{generation}}'\\n.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/review/iterations/iteration-002.md:1829:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/review/iterations/iteration-001.md:3154:.opencode/commands/spec_kit/assets/spec_kit_deep-review_confirm.yaml:181:            append_jsonl: '{\\\"type\\\":\\\"event\\\",\\\"event\\\":\\\"restarted\\\",\\\"mode\\\":\\\"review\\\",\\\"sessionId\\\":\\\"{session_id}\\\",\\\"parentSessionId\\\":\\\"{prior_session_id}\\\",\\\"lineageMode\\\":\\\"restart\\\",\\\"generation\\\":{generation},\\\"archivedPath\\\":\\\"{spec_folder}/review_archive/{timestamp_slug}\\\",\\\"timestamp\\\":\\\"{ISO_8601_NOW}\\\"}'\\n.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/review/iterations/iteration-002.md:1831:.open