 ran same-class producer, consumer, and prompt-artifact path inventories."},{"id":"r4-r7-r3-flow","status":"pass","evidence":"findingClass, scopeProof, and affectedSurfaceHints flow from review findingDetails into R7 Planning Packet synthesis and both R3 plan modes' FIX ADDENDUM import/render guidance."},{"id":"direct-command-injection","status":"pass","evidence":"No direct shell/eval execution of affectedSurfacesSeed, activeFindings, findingClass, scopeProof, or affectedSurfaceHints was found in the R3 plan workflow surfaces inspected."},{"id":"prompt-injection-boundary","status":"fail","evidence":"The same fields are imported into planner context without explicit data-only handling, quoting, escaping, truncation, or hostile-content rejection guidance."},{"id":"path-leak-check","status":"partial","evidence":"No absolute workspace paths were found in the R3/R7 command templates inspected; active 010 review prompt artifacts retain absolute /Users/... output paths."}]},"coverage":{"sameClassProducerInventory":true,"crossConsumerFlow":true,"matrixCompleteness":false,"securityPromptSurface":true,"pathLeakInventory":true},"noveltyJustification":"Security re-verification found the field handoff closed but identified one prompt-injection boundary gap and one persisted prompt path disclosure advisory.","ruledOut":["missing R4 findingClass/scopeProof production guidance","missing R7 Planning Packet field synthesis guidance","missing R3 FIX ADDENDUM import guidance","direct shell execution of affected surface fields in R3 plan workflow","absolute workspace path leak in R3/R7 command templates inspected"],"budgetProfile":{"toolCallsUsed":12,"mode":"leaf"},"newFindingsRatio":0.35,"sessionId":"2026-05-02T19:37:23Z","generation":1,"lineageMode":"new","timestamp":"2026-05-02T19:45:48Z","durationMs":0}
