.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/004-runtime-executor-hardening/001-foundational-runtime/research/research.md:1083:5. **R46-001 -- `COMMAND_BRIDGES` prefix collapse** (`skill_advisor.py:980-1021, 1404-1410, 1647, 1741-1768`; `test_skill_advisor.py:73-186`). `COMMAND_BRIDGES` registers only `/spec_kit` and `spec_kit:` prefix markers. `detect_explicit_command_intent()` stops at first containment match. All `/spec_kit:*` subcommands collapse to `command-spec-kit` at `kind_priority=2`. Live consequence: `/spec_kit:deep-research` -> `command-spec-kit` 0.95, `sk-deep-research` 0.70.
