.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/004-runtime-executor-hardening/002-sk-deep-cli-runtime-execution/implementation-summary.md:72:**What shipped:** Executor selection for `sk-deep-research` + `sk-deep-review` as a branch INSIDE the existing YAML `step_dispatch_iteration` (not a loop replacement). Preserves all skill-owned invariants (state ownership, reducer exclusivity, convergence detection, lifecycle events) while enabling `codex exec` dispatch with `gpt-5.4 + reasoning-effort=high + service-tier=fast`.
