ment-counting behavior in shell validators; F004 is the default orchestration and coverage path omitting those validators.","No new placeholder, template-source, template-header, or anchor finding; those validators do not count marker comments as semantic evidence.","No P0 security, data-loss, or destructive runtime behavior found."],"focusTrack":"validator-coverage","convergenceSignals":{"rollingAvg":0.21,"madScore":0.06,"dimensionCoverage":0.8,"compositeStop":0.0},"executor":{"kind":"cli-copilot","model":"gpt-5.5","requestedReasoningEffort":"high"}}
